{"tid":1687686,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【BZ 19】為《爐石戰記》選手聰哥事件抗議玩家在 BlizzCon 會場聚集 高舉聲援 T 恤和標語","createTime":"2019-11-02T04:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T07:54:00.000Z","uid":109923,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5a2d7009a5b0ce3e05c2223b1fd14fc1c1fa65","tid":1687686,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"隨著 BlizzCon 2019 即將開展，目前已有玩家為《爐石戰記》選手 Blitzchung（聰哥）事件抗議的玩家紛紛在展場外聚集，並高舉聲援標語並贈送相關 T 恤。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yddKoE7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyddKoE7.jpg&h=3a11c218&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/02/121208_cad4ab035572d135e6cee19ef1f8d9ba.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F02%2F121208_cad4ab035572d135e6cee19ef1f8d9ba.jpeg&h=38b57201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n　　今年 10 月，Blizzard 因《爐石戰記》聰哥事件裁決引發軒然大波，部分抗議團體宣稱將會到場進行抗議，而隨著年度盛會 BlizzCon 2019 即將開幕，展場外已陸續有玩家集結，其中更包括因《爐石戰記》聰哥事件而決定挺身聲援的抗議玩家。<br />\n <br />\n　　玩家在場外高舉著香港旗幟，並發放印有小美的「光復香港，時代革命」標語、雨傘貼紙，以及寫著「小美與香港同在（Mei With Hong Kong）」和Blizzard 核心價值「重視每個意見、負責任的領導、放眼全球（Every Voice Matters, Lead Responsibly, Think Globally）」的 T 恤等。<br />\n <br />\n　　據了解，抗議玩家在會場外送 T 恤和標語，有玩家自己發起、也有由自由香港贊助的，有女性玩家更身穿小熊維尼裝聲援；此外，還有美國玩家主動向前詢問是否需要捐錢，而抗議團體回應：「不用，但請支持香港！」<br />\n <br />\n※備註：小美為 Blizzard 旗下射擊遊戲《鬥陣特攻》的英雄角色，許多歐美玩家以該名角色進行二次創作來聲援香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A9g0Gsy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA9g0Gsy.jpg&h=7b13e271&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KO6B0U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KO6B0U.jpg&h=9610124c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fb4ULUf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffb4ULUf.jpg&h=fb0f2964&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ajoa3FV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fajoa3FV.jpg&h=06596589&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Co2UNC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Co2UNC.jpg&h=5f5df6fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbp5Szi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frbp5Szi.jpg&h=b56d051f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98LQjem.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98LQjem.jpg&h=1ac22cc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場有美國警察在維護秩序<br />\n<br />\n　　BlizzCon 2019 即將在台灣時間半夜 2 時登場，根據抗議團體指出，預計下午（活動當地時間）還會有更多團體會到場。"},{"pid":"5dbd23aa86d6f14c44f93f0dabfdc4055e788fc8","tid":1687686,"uid":48742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T04:24:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c8b85ffefc383b1fd059f77792870398a4005583","tid":1687686,"uid":18333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T04:54:07.000Z","msg":"個個玩D4 了， 冇人理"},{"pid":"5703be13c3226b666c73a968c34670be5d8d64e1","tid":1687686,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:01:50.000Z","msg":"但聽聞聰哥好似玩返爐石?<br />\n如果係真，被波及嗰兩個台灣直播主都好慘"},{"pid":"c90428661e2993453156ff4166b6084e4096a19b","tid":1687686,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5703be13c3226b666c73a968c34670be5d8d64e1","tid":1687686,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:01:50.000Z","msg":"但聽聞聰哥好似玩返爐石?<br />\n如果係真，被波及嗰兩個台灣直播主都好慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XF4JEvS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXF4JEvS.jpg&h=5fcfe18b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個台灣直播主仲撐佢<br />\n但佢自己喺最新嘅回覆都話自己畀人炒咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fs9p8pq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffs9p8pq.jpg&h=ba40ae7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"481fb8937a9c2dea2b2b31c8f72